{"tid":1233784,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋到底知唔知重點係乜嘢？","createTime":"2019-06-16T21:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:08:04.000Z","uid":101824,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10a1385ed900302bc01913d3b48428444d445daa","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:54:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">策略</span><br />\n集會 遊行 佔領 衝擊 不合作運動<br />\n呢啲都係抗爭嘅方法<br />\n但關鍵在於 點樣用一連續嘅方法逼使政府撤修例<br />\n其實而家就好似loop緊<br />\n雖然今日比上禮拜係有更多嘅人出嚟<br />\n但之後呢？？？<br />\n如果政府唔回應 你地又會點做呀？<br />\n我地應該要再將行動升級 <br />\n再次佔領 一直罷工罷課 <br />\n而唔係慢慢忘記呢件事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地贏就贏 輸就輸 冇輸一半呢件事</span>"},{"pid":"04baac0c32607851d4b2f400913137332405c65a","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:57:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"36e8cc6b48182f50ac4c5d170b2999822aedb096","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:01:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"097c2180680cf2b066a2ea14cc4fe76cc9942bad","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d3a5cda3808ad0f96c85b056214f228097d94a","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52823ed494df0124d20957d019c4d8a4c3099a99","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1e7b548cc3ff8a52dbf78d0456906f552abb7b","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T22:14:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"776dd17b18ac6c329f741ab08fa1ea8eb9de5fbb","tid":1233784,"uid":101824,"like":